params.1319:
The Corporeal Beast is a group boss that can be found residing in its cave found east of the Graveyard of Shadows in the Wilderness.

Attack Styles - Melee, Magic, Special.
Immunities - Poison, Venom
Slayer categories - None
params.1320:
There are no mandatory requirements to fight the Corporeal Beast.

Combat Achievement task difficulty:
- Elite
- Master
